%F A342707 T(7, k) = k^k + k + 1 = A066279(k).
%F A342707 T(16, k) = k^k^k = A002488(k).
%F A342707 T(m + n, k) = T(m, k) + T(n, k) when m AND n = 0 (where AND denotes the bitwise AND operator).
